{
  "stem": "8234.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Later on, I knew that they went to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, I was picked with 40, and they put us on trains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went to another camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's irony-- four kilometers from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They call it Adrzejow, also a Jewish camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Yeah, a matter of fact, we only Jews, Polish Jews, only Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a Jewish camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we cleared-- there was a forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had to cut the trees.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the head of the camp was also a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Until-- there was-- there was a woman camp too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Just close, a woman camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I-- I met my cousin over here, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we worked-- was it '42?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Til [? end of ?] '42, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was winter, I remember, when they liquidated that camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we couldn't work in the snow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was sent to Birkenau, Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Winter of what year?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By-- by cattle train, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't went to the [? train ?], like people tell me, there was no women or no children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that took us off from the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, another thing, the guys-- which was the commander-- took us on the train, recognized a few guys from Posen, and they recognize me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one was over there and says, hey, Ralph, you know who is here?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he gave me the name of Husley.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Husley was a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We slept in the same-- he slept above me in Gutenbrunn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says he's-- he's a [NON-ENGLISH] in the bakery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just tell him about me, tell him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well they took us to the barrack-- over there was a selection, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember that guy in the white uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Murderer-- left, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, we went into camp-- Which guy was that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was '42.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
